CBRE is delighted to offer, for lease, Lot 9 Production Way, Pakenham.

This property is exceptionally located in South East Business Estate, providing immediate access to Koo Wee Rup Road and Princes Freeway (M1). This location is home to many household names including Car Megamart and Total Tools, a testament to its attractive location.

Property Details:
+ Industrial 1 Zone
+ Warehouse area: 1,054sqm*
+ Single level office area: 106sqm*
+ Total building area: 1,160sqm*
+ Total land area: 1,751sqm*
+ Modern concrete tilt slab premises
+ Corporate office amenity including heating/cooling, kitchen, toilet and shower
+ Container height roller door
+ 3 phase power
+ 17 car spaces

Please enquire within for building plans and private inspections:

Ned Murphy - ned.murphy@cbre.com.au

Lachlan Ferguson - lachlan.ferguson@cbre.com.au

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to offer for sale or lease, Lot 13 Commercial Drive, Pakenham.
 
The property is exceptionally located with convenient access to the Princes Freeway (M1) via McGregor Rd and Koo Wee Rup Rd on/off ramps.
 
Property features include:
+ Warehouse area 2,535sqm* - high clearance offering excellent cubic capacity
+ Dual level corporate office area 280sqm* - first class finishes
+ Total building area 2,815sqm*
+ Total land area 4,260sqm*
+ Loading canopy with associated hardstand
+ Five (5) container height roller doors.
+ 45 on-site car parking spaces
+ Minutes from Princes Highway.
 
Please enquire within for building plans and private inspections.
 
*approx.

CBRE is excited to offer 94 Sette Court, Pakenham, for lease.

This site is well located on Sette Court with direct access onto Exchange Drive, connecting the property to nearby major arterials including Koo Wee Rup Road and Princes Freeway.

This location is home to many household names including Car Megamart and Total Tools, a testament to its attractive location.

Property features include:
+ Site area of: 3,353sqm*
+ Total building area: 2,035sqm*
+ 1,888sqm* of high clearance, clear span warehouse
+ Four (4) container height roller shutter doors
+ All-weather loading canopy
+ 147sqm* of well-presented, single level corporate office area
+ End of trip facilities and shower
+ Side yard with canopy cover
+ Electric gated security and landscaped garden

*approx.
